==English==
===Noun phrase===
'''[[fast]] [[food]]''' (''uncountable'')

#A type of meal that is often pre-prepared and served quickly.
#A type of food that is quickly made, but of low nutritional value; [[junk food]].

<!-- not adj but noun used attributively -  shouldn't this be hyphenated anyway?
===Adjective phrase===
'''[[fast]] [[food]]'''
#used to describe an establishment serving this kind of food
#*'''''Fast food''' [[restaurant]]s are often [[inexpensive]].''
-->

